{"title":"Is the untrained NS teacher worth even less than we thought?: NS teacher endorsement of folk beliefs in EFL education","link":"https://iafor.org/is-the-untrained-ns-teacher-worth-even-less-than-we-thought/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=is-the-untrained-ns-teacher-worth-even-less-than-we-thought","date":1567741490000,"content":"<p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Dr Charles Allen Brown, Hokkaido University, Japan\" srcset=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-150x150.jpg 150w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-600x600.jpg 600w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-100x100.jpg 100w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-50x50.jpg 50w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-300x300.jpg 300w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Dr-Charles-Allen-Brown-Hokkaido-University-Japan-32x32.jpg 32w\" />In this presentation, Dr Charles Allen Brown discusses how his own multi-year ethnographic fieldwork examining ground-level practices of English education in Japan and Taiwan indicates that the untrained NS teacher may be even less valuable than is commonly assumed.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://iafor.org/is-the-untrained-ns-teacher-worth-even-less-than-we-thought/\">Is the untrained NS teacher worth even less than we thought?: NS teacher endorsement of folk beliefs in EFL education</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://iafor.org\">The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)</a>.</p>","author":"IAFOR","siteTitle":"The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)","siteHash":"db6175d8277e1d8dd86d5cc607b1dd9335cce255aa7e00b46d0931f23a0d47f6","entryHash":"8